    <!-- Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)-->
    <link href="css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        .mySlides {
            display: none;
        }

        .carosel_button {
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color: lightgray;
            color: black;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 4px 2px;
            transition-duration: 0.4s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .carosel_button:hover {
                background-color: yellow;
                color: black;
            }
        /* Labels for checked inputs */
        input[type="checkbox"] {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
        }

        input:checked + span {
            color: darkorange;
        }

        input[type="checkbox"]:checked {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px yellow;
        }

        /* The Modal (background) */
        .modal {
            display: none; /* Hidden by default */
            position: fixed; /* Stay in place */
            z-index: 1; /* Sit on top */
            padding-top: 100px; /* Location of the box */
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%; /* Full width */
            height: 100%; /* Full height */
            overflow: auto; /* Enable scroll if needed */
            background-color: rgb(0,0,0); /* Fallback color */
            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); /* Black w/ opacity */
        }

        /* Modal Content */
        .modal-content {
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color: #fefefe;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #888;
            width: 80%;
        }

        /* The Close Button */
        .close {
            color: #aaaaaa;
            float: right;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

            .close:hover,
            .close:focus {
                color: #000;
                text-decoration: none;
                cursor: pointer;
            }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation-->
    <!-- Page Header-->
    <!-- Page Header-->
    <header class="masthead" style="background-image: url('../../assets/img/sunglasses1.png')">
        <div class="container position-relative px-4 px-lg-5">
            <div class="row gx-4 gx-lg-5 justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-10 col-xl-10">
                    <div class="page-heading">
                        <h1>Sun Glasses</h1>
                        <span class="subheading">It is important to protect our children’s eyes.</span>
                        <br />
                        <span class="subheading">As parents we should always remember to wear sunglasses for our children, because our children are particularly sensitive to UV radiation, skin and eye damage. </span>
                        <br />
                        <span class="subheading">Once children are old enough to manage wearing sunglasses, they should be encouraged to do so when doing outdoor activities.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Post Content-->
    <!-- Section: Design block -->
    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center mt-5">
                <div class="col-lg-9">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body p-5">
                            <div class="w3-content w3-display-container">
                                <div class='mySlides'>
                                    <h3 class="section-heading" id="why">Why Sunglasses?</h3>

                                    <p>UV radiation causes both temporary and chronic eye damages when our eyes are exposed to it frequently.</p>
                                    <p>When the UV level is 3 or above, the Cancer Council suggests wearing sunglasses at all times. </p>
                                    <p>During the summer in Australia, all regions of the nation are exposed to UV levels of 3 or higher for lengthy periods of time during the day. </p>
                                    <p>When the sun is low in the sky, our eyes are exposed to UV radiation directly. Reflected and scattered light also have a strong impact and increase the total UV radiation that is exposed to our eyes.</p>

                                    <table class="table table-striped">
                                        <thead>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th scope="col">Lens Category</th>
                                                <th scope="col">Description</th>
                                            </tr>
                                        </thead>
                                        <tbody>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td scope="row">Category 0</td>
                                                <td>Light tint sunglasses or fashion spectacles</td>
                                                <td><button class="carosel_button" id="len_0">Open</button></td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td scope="row">Category 1</td>
                                                <td>Light tint sunglasses or fashion spectacles</td>
                                                <td><button class="carosel_button" id="len_1">Open</button></td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td scope="row">Category 2</td>
                                                <td>General purpose sunglasses</td>
                                                <td><button class="carosel_button" id="len_2">Open</button></td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td scope="row">Category 3</td>
                                                <td>General purpose sunglasses</td>
                                                <td><button class="carosel_button" id="len_3">Open</button></td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td scope="row">Category 4</td>
                                                <td>Very dark special sunglasses – very high sunglare reduction</td>
                                                <td><button class="carosel_button" id="len_4">Open</button></td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </tbody>
                                    </table>

                                    <div id="len_0_content" class="modal">
                                        <!-- Modal content -->
                                        <div class="modal-content">
                                            <span class="close" id="close_0">&times;</span>
                                            <label><b>Category 0:</b><br> Provide very limited reduction of sunglare and some UV proteciton.</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div id="len_1_content" class="modal">
                                        <!-- Modal content -->
                                        <div class="modal-content">
                                            <span class="close" id="close_1">&times;</span>
                                            <label><b>Category 1:</b><br> Provide limited protection against sunglare and some UV protection; they are not suitable for driving in at night or under dull light conditions.</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div id="len_2_content" class="modal">
                                        <!-- Modal content -->
                                        <div class="modal-content">
                                            <span class="close" id="close_2">&times;</span>
                                            <label><b>Category 2:</b><br> Provide good protection against sunglare and good UV protection; they suitable for driving in at night or under dull light conditions.</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div id="len_3_content" class="modal">
                                        <!-- Modal content -->
                                        <div class="modal-content">
                                            <span class="close" id="close_3">&times;</span>
                                            <label><b>Category 3:</b><br> Provide high protection against sunglare and good UV protection; they are not suitable for driving at night or under dull light conditions.</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div id="len_4_content" class="modal">
                                        <!-- Modal content -->
                                        <div class="modal-content">
                                            <span class="close" id="close_4">&times;</span>
                                            <label><b>Category 4:</b><br> Special purpose sunglasses that provide a very high protection against extreme sun glare and good UV protection, they are not suitable for road use and driving.</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                </div>

                                <div class='mySlides'>
                                    <h3 class="section-heading" id="Tips">Tips for Parents</h3>
                                    <p><input type="checkbox">&nbsp;<span>Always put a pair of sunglasses in your children’s bag, so they can put on when needed.</span></p>
                                    <p><input type="checkbox">&nbsp;<span>Choose a close-fitting, wrap-around style of sunglasses for your children.</span></p>
                                    <p><input type="checkbox">&nbsp;<span>Choose category 2 or higher glasses for your children as lenses with category above 2 can absorb more than 95% of UV radiation and provide a good protection for your children.</span></p>
                                    <p><input type="checkbox">&nbsp;<span>Do not use toy sunglasses for your children, as they do not meet the sun protection requirements under the Australian Standard.</span></p>
                                    <p><input type="checkbox">&nbsp;<span>Choose sunglasses that have soft elastic to keep the glasses in place. Also, choose a style that is safe for children to use, e.g. make sure the arms of glasses don't become a safety hazard.</span></p>
                                    <p><input type="checkbox">&nbsp;<span>If your children don’t want to wear sunglasses, put on a suitable hat can still help protect their eyes from the damage of UV radiation.</span></p>
                                </div>
                                <span class="caption text-muted">
                                    <button class="carosel_button" onclick="plusDivs(-1)">❮</button>
                                    <button class="carosel_button" onclick="plusDivs(1)">❯</button>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
